* Pooland: (danh từ) - Ba Lan (quốc gia)
	+ Meaning: Poland is a country located in Central Europe.
	+ Example sentence: "I'm planning to visit Poland next year."
	+ Related words: Polish, Warsaw, Europe
	+ Antonyms: None

Note: Poland is a country, so it doesn't have antonyms.
